name: AxoPinguix Especial Edition
description:
We all have a reference, a point of inspiration to create anything, I started creating NFTs very recently, on the way I discovered Pinguix and I loved what he does, from that moment my admiration and respect were growing and today I have created this tribute, as a form of gratitude, I hope you like it. 

You can follow Pinguix: @PinguixNFT
